"2 cups uncooked orecchiette (about 8 ounces uncooked","3 cups chopped plum tomato","1 1/4 cups (5 ounces) diced fresh mozzarella cheese","1 cup loosely packed chopped fresh basil","1 tablespoon extravirgin olive oil","3/4 teaspoon salt","1/4 teaspoon crushed red pepper","2  garlic cloves, minced"